{"sessionId":"a1ab4ca4-1896-4893-af37-884d5fad9b63","actor":"agent","type":"agent.message","payload":{"text":"Once upon a time in a quaint village nestled between two majestic mountains, there lived a curious girl named Elara. Elara possessed a unique gift; she could communicate with the creatures of the forest. Every day after her chores, she would venture into the woods, where she was greeted by birds that chirped lively tales, rabbits that shared secrets of the underbrush, and wise old owls that offered her guidance.

